line_1: Ah, Jockey, ill advisest thou, I wis,
line_2: To think of songs at such a time as this.

line_1: " Not needeth Proof: To prove it were, I wis,
line_2: " Perfection forms, and with Perfection Bliss.

line_1: " Not needeth Proof: To prove it were, I wis,
line_2: "To prove the beauteous World excels the brute Abyss.
